title: New Venture Challenge Women's Entrepreneurship Prize Fund
description: To provide stipends as awards for students who win the Women's Entrepreneurship track of the NVC competition and general administrative support of the Women's Entrepreneurship Prize of the NVC at the Leeds School of Business.
